description: David Gorden is a graphic novelist and comic artist. He currently works for Lion Forge Comics writing such titles Quincredible, Trimaxx, Rampage Jackson: Street Soldier, and Airwolf. When he’s not creating harrowing adventures or attempting to solve the mysteries of the universe he likes to spend his spare time playing spades and enjoying the company of family and friends. You can reach him on twitter @dkg72 and on Facebook at www.facebook.com/DavidGorden72.
name: David Gorden

description:
Michael Frizell is a writer for Bluewater, which publishes biographical comics about celebrities, political figures, and historical personages of note. Frizell lives in Springfield, Missouri, where he also works in the adult education field. He is a fan of comicdom as well as a writer, and the walls of his office in which he works are decorated with graded issues of Marvel's original Star Wars series, The Micronauts, and Rom, comics from his childhood that he valued.

His brother, David, is a talented artist, who is also based out of the southwest Missouri area.
name: Michael L. Frizell
